The full implementation code:


Our plugin solution is very similar with 
Bootstrap

data-api
 syntax. It's a modular way to organize the initialize script for the 3rd plugin.
Just like 
Bootstrap

data-api
 usage, add 
data-plugin="{plugin name}"
 to element and add 
[data-{options}]
 to element. The components will be initialized.


